			<DIV>Personally...I would like to see the breaking down of blocks to small peices be more rewarding...</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I mean...1 block to 1 large brick, yet 3 large bricks to 1 block?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>In all honesty, I think it should go like this: 1 block breaks down into 2 Large bricks, 1 Large brick breaks down into 2 small bricks, and 1 small brick breaks down into 2 OR 3 (whichever) small peices...</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>It would honestly just make much more sense - you still wouldn't be able to just up and recombine your result into the higher lvl - because 2 large bricks wouldn't make a block - 3 would <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-happy.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Just a thought <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-very-happy.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0></DIV>
